{"tid":1299423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【勿中伏】不要自亂陣腳，重整旗鼓，面對「壽終正寢」","createTime":"2019-07-09T05:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T07:45:20.000Z","uid":36073,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3104eefa3759f84f8b1e6b0d928005958c219c2f","tid":1299423,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:04:46.000Z","msg":"林鄭一個四字成語「壽終正寢」，打散咗我哋盤旗<br />\n<br />\n出面已經有唔同聲音<br />\n一方認為「壽終正寢」與「撒回」無關，唯有正式撒回才能符合法律<br />\n另一方認為繼續針對「壽終正寢」與「撒回」只會令人覺得咬著唔放，應該轉向其他訴求<br />\n<br />\n林鄭今次仲要表明，接受與學生代表公開對話，雙方不應有前設<br />\n等同令民意變為「唔接受對話，就係你班學生嘅錯」<br />\n<br />\n各位應該要承認，我哋今舖已經中咗林鄭嘅分化策略，目標將槍頭轉向我哋，令我哋受到溫和中間派聲音嘅打擊，另外企圖消磨港人抗爭意志<br />\n<br />\n無論如何<br />\n我依然相信群眾力量，當冇大台冇代表，自然有不同聲音出現，呢個係民主嘅一部份<br />\n但係我哋唔好亂，首要討論下一步行動同訴求，冷靜處理，切忌因為一時怒氣沖昏而強硬行動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不分化，不篤灰，不割蓆<br />\n齊上齊落"},{"pid":"50061787e4e8f9d4441d20bdaf2ee32e0ce34eb3","tid":1299423,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:05:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"719ff106ebd96dd20410f1b28cb8edfb83919277","tid":1299423,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:05:18.000Z","msg":"全力追究黑警"},{"pid":"03b4bdb5c4dee0b10a9036562e5e43f3d58877dc","tid":1299423,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:05:44.000Z","msg":"<code></code>"},{"pid":"e52412bd24c31a5bc4bec9fb6a00f0caafd61c6c","tid":1299423,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"[一圖睇哂]警隊大撚哂 保安局部隊化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1298620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1298620</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3c78a6b0a0cc27c74942c79c6856f1c5ab8c32db","tid":1299423,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:06:07.000Z","msg":"一日不撤回修例，有關草案都彌留在恢復二讀狀態"},{"pid":"26460989c41cf107e2511bb04ef3a83e3c65ba7a","tid":1299423,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:06:32.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e17822ae2e92b5f09e2a8761e5540feb36117bfd","tid":1299423,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:06:36.000Z","msg":"調查委員會"},{"pid":"99a415edf7daa6ab56a743355fce741bad75a10e","tid":1299423,"uid":170426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:07:07.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">七大訴求<br />\n齊上齊落</span></span>"},{"pid":"366686b537fb87cfec3c89f50a4a16c95875af5e","tid":1299423,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:45:20.000Z","msg":"推"}]}